           <gco:CharacterString>The AgSat Areas of Interest map contains area polygons where satellite imagery will be collected for the Farm Service Agency (FSA) to provide imagery coverage for FSA business to include image base replacement, torando damage assessment, and drought assessment. The map shows areas of interest that have been awarded (green) and areas that were planned for but did not get awarded (tan). This imagery is collected under a satellite blanket purchase agreement created for FSA by the Aerial Photography Field Office in Salt Lake City. For more information about this program please contact the contracting officer Jacque La Croix. Click on the bookmark tab in the map to zoom to each area of interest on the map. Click on a polygon inside the map to display an informational popup.</gco:CharacterString>          </gmd:abstract>          <gmd:purpose>             <gco:CharacterString>To provide a public coverage map of areas of interest for the FSA satellite blanket purchase agreement so that agencies know what is already being collected and duplication of effort can be reduced.</gco:CharacterString> and Attribute Overview: The map layers: AK SLI Planned, AgSat AK 2013 End of Year Awarded, AgSat Alabama Awarded, AgSat Alaska Awarded, AgSat Arkansas Awarded, AgSat Arkansas Planned, AgSat Georgia Planned, Agsat Hawaii Awarded, Agsat USVI Awarded contain the following fields and attributes - Area Name - used to denote area of interest which may or may not be at the state or county level. Image Use - primary business use for planning purposes. Spatial Resolution - pixel size. Spectral Resolution - range of wavelength available in the image. Bit Depth - range of values a raster can store, standard for this program is 8 bit. Cloud Cover - up to 10% is the standard specification for this program. No Data - standard for this program is no data is not acceptable. Acquisition window - the date for the desired acquisition of the imagery, this may be a range or general date. Square Miles - Area of interest approximate coverage area in square miles. Entity and Attribute Detail Citation: The attribute values for all AgSat areas of interest were derived from the FSA satellite blanket purchase agreement information.</gco:CharacterString>
